523
00:28:04,891 --> 00:28:07,060
I did it, I did it, then I made a U-turn.

524
00:28:08,269 --> 00:28:09,104
uh?

525
00:28:10,188 --> 00:28:11,189
Divorced

526
00:28:12,982 --> 00:28:13,983
[Bona] Um...

527
00:28:15,902 --> 00:28:17,445
But this is ‘no kids’

528
00:28:18,446 --> 00:28:19,364
what do you mean?

529
00:28:21,408 --> 00:28:23,576
This is a movement that started in Paris.

530
00:28:23,660 --> 00:28:27,622
Even people who don't like kids shouldn't feel guilty.

531
00:28:30,458 --> 00:28:31,459
Do you hate kids?

532
00:28:31,543 --> 00:28:33,169
Yeah, I hate it

533
00:28:37,966 --> 00:28:40,593
- You think it's strange too - Huh?

534
00:28:40,677 --> 00:28:43,555
[Bona] There are people who look at me strangely when I say I hate kids.

535
00:28:43,638 --> 00:28:46,891
Ah, no~ Those people are strange.

536
00:28:46,975 --> 00:28:48,393
Do you really think so?

537
00:28:48,476 --> 00:28:49,352
of course

538
00:28:51,771 --> 00:28:53,606
