[Whispering] Let’s have fun with this girl first.

542
00:29:10,081 --> 00:29:12,000
- [Bright music] - [Seungmin/Laughing] Ah, it tickles.

543
00:29:32,562 --> 00:29:35,982
[Seungmin] Ha, it feels like a dream for a day like this to come.

544
00:29:36,065 --> 00:29:37,650
[Bona] Actually, I was a little scared.

545
00:29:37,734 --> 00:29:38,735
[Seungmin] Why?

546
00:29:38,818 --> 00:29:40,904
[Bona] I wonder if my brother will get married and have children.

547
00:29:46,785 --> 00:29:48,912
[Thump - Keyboard]

548
00:29:51,706 --> 00:29:52,916
[Seungmin] But who says you don’t have children?

549
00:29:55,376 --> 00:29:58,004
I said it before, divorced and no kids.

550
00:29:58,087 --> 00:29:59,464
[Seungmin] Ah~

551
00:30:04,093 --> 00:30:04,969
Where are you going!

552
00:30:06,679 --> 00:30:07,680
Where are you going!

553
00:30:15,814 --> 00:30:18,358
Just because I didn't say anything doesn't mean it's not there

554
00:30:18,441 --> 00:30:20,610
- [Bona] Um, it's the same - No.

555
00:30:23,738 --> 00:30:25,073
- [Bona] Wait a minute - Yes, um

556
00:30:25,156 --> 00:30:27,283
- Wait, wait, wait - Uh, why?

557
00:30:27,367 --> 00:30:28,701
[Bona] Wait a minute! wait for a sec

558
00:30:29,869 --> 00:30:31,496
Are you saying it exists or doesn’t exist?

559
00:30:32,580 --> 00:30:33,706
baby?

560
00:30:34,541 --> 00:30:35,542
me?

561
