573
00:31:37,520 --> 00:31:40,148
Enough to captivate one of our writers, huh?

574
00:31:41,566 --> 00:31:44,152
Well, just a friendly style?

575
00:31:44,235 --> 00:31:46,529
Sweet and handsome, huh?

576
00:31:47,614 --> 00:31:50,825
He's handsome and has a romantic side.

577
00:31:52,285 --> 00:31:54,746
My brother was in a band in college.

578
00:31:54,829 --> 00:31:59,208
He even invited me to a performance to sing a song for me.

579
00:31:59,292 --> 00:32:00,418
[Woman] Isn’t it so cool?

580
00:32:00,501 --> 00:32:01,920
So what did you think of the song?

581
00:32:02,795 --> 00:32:04,923
Uh... the song...

582
00:32:05,006 --> 00:32:06,382
- I didn't hear - Why?

583
