It's just that something happened to my brother at that time.

584
00:32:08,968 --> 00:32:10,678
[Woman] No, what’s the matter?

585
00:32:12,639 --> 00:32:13,932
unavoidable circumstances

586
00:32:14,015 --> 00:32:15,099
[Employee] You are here

587
00:32:18,811 --> 00:32:20,063
[Bona] Hello, Kyung-ah.

588
00:32:20,146 --> 00:32:22,607
Oh my, author, wow, it’s been a really long time.

589
00:32:22,690 --> 00:32:24,943
We met last time at the Paris collection.

590
00:32:25,026 --> 00:32:27,028
- You remember me, right? - Oh, I remember.

591
00:32:27,111 --> 00:32:29,364
[Kyungah] Real photo from the cover of France’s ‘Elle’

592
00:32:29,447 --> 00:32:31,491
Wow, it was so artistic.

593
00:32:31,574 --> 00:32:32,742
It was so good, right?

594
00:32:35,078 --> 00:32:36,412
