however

647
00:34:45,833 --> 00:34:48,628
If I'm lying to you or anything like that

648
00:34:49,337 --> 00:34:50,338
He's a married man

649
00:34:51,214 --> 00:34:53,758
No, ah, ah, not like that, ah, not like that.

650
00:34:53,841 --> 00:34:56,719
Oh, I'm really sure they got divorced, no, no.

651
00:34:57,845 --> 00:35:00,181
I also have something important to tell you.

652
00:35:00,264 --> 00:35:02,725
- [Running steps] - [Child] Ah, bro! Oh, give it to me quickly!

653
00:35:03,601 --> 00:35:04,602
Oh, really

654
