- [Woman] Stop fooling around... - Uh.

655
00:35:07,772 --> 00:35:09,398
When I was young

656
00:35:09,482 --> 00:35:12,819
I was very lonely because I spent a lot of time alone.

657
00:35:13,778 --> 00:35:16,280
Meeting new people while working

658
00:35:16,364 --> 00:35:18,116
It's nice to wander around

659
00:35:18,991 --> 00:35:20,159
Something in my heart

660
00:35:21,119 --> 00:35:22,245
[clatter]

661
00:35:22,328 --> 00:35:24,539
- Should I say that something was missing? - [The children are noisy]

662
00:35:24,622 --> 00:35:26,165
- [Child 1] Bang, bang, bang - [Child 2] Grrrr!

663
00:35:27,542 --> 00:35:28,960
[Child 1] Shoo, Shoo, Shoo!

664
00:35:29,669 --> 00:35:31,379
I still envy you

665
00:35:31,462 --> 00:35:32,922
[Child 2] Oh, I won!

666
00:35:33,005 --> 00:35:34,674
[Seungmin] You do what you want to do

667
00:35:34,757 --> 00:35:35,633
Well, my dream has come true

668
00:35:37,051 --> 00:35:38,052
however

669
