I'm curious too

672
00:35:51,649 --> 00:35:53,609
So what I want to say is

673
00:35:54,360 --> 00:35:57,864
I felt really empty inside, but I met my brother recently.

674
00:36:00,032 --> 00:36:01,492
I feel so filled

675
