thank you

676
00:36:08,833 --> 00:36:10,710
What did you want to say?

677
00:36:10,793 --> 00:36:12,461
- [Child 1] Give it to me quickly! - [Child 2] Oh, I hate it!

678
00:36:12,545 --> 00:36:14,463
[Child 1] Give it to me! madam

679
00:36:14,547 --> 00:36:16,007
- [Child 2] I hate it! - [Child 1] Oh, that’s really true.

680
00:36:16,090 --> 00:36:17,884
Oh, give it to me quickly!

681
00:36:17,967 --> 00:36:20,761
- Ah, give it to me quickly - [Child 2] Ah, why~

682
00:36:20,845 --> 00:36:22,388
- [Child 1] Oh, that's right - Ah...

683
00:36:24,724 --> 00:36:26,976
