684
00:36:28,519 --> 00:36:30,062
Here, wait a minute.

685
00:36:30,146 --> 00:36:31,397
Do you need anything?

686
00:36:31,480 --> 00:36:34,275
We came here because we wanted to talk quietly.

687
00:36:34,358 --> 00:36:35,610
I think it's a bit too much

688
00:36:35,693 --> 00:36:38,404
Everyone here is talking quietly while following etiquette.

689
00:36:38,487 --> 00:36:41,199
I think they're just so inconsiderate.

690
