703
00:37:27,745 --> 00:37:28,996
no, dad is good

704
00:37:29,789 --> 00:37:30,957
I'm afraid you'll have a hard time

705
00:37:31,457 --> 00:37:33,501
- It’s not difficult at all? - okay

706
