[Soyoung] Now, it’s done.

707
00:37:42,927 --> 00:37:44,345
[Seungmin] Isn’t that tent too small for you?

708
00:37:45,012 --> 00:37:46,138
Is it still good?

709
00:37:46,722 --> 00:37:49,267
How about donating? Give it to someone who needs it more

710
00:37:49,350 --> 00:37:51,477
Oh, should I give it to mom’s house? My little brother is coming soon

711
