714
00:37:59,902 --> 00:38:00,987
Why are you doing this?

715
00:38:01,070 --> 00:38:03,406
No, I'm just trying to create some space.

716
00:38:03,489 --> 00:38:04,615
A place to put new things

717
00:38:04,699 --> 00:38:06,492
I don't need new stuff

718
00:38:06,575 --> 00:38:08,119
Who says tents are small?

719
