See, it goes with mango too.

720
00:38:14,583 --> 00:38:16,794
- Is it really comfortable? - okay

721
00:38:16,877 --> 00:38:20,131
[Soyoung] Promise me you won’t give away my tent, it’s mine.

722
00:38:20,214 --> 00:38:21,215
[Seungmin] I got it

723
00:38:22,383 --> 00:38:23,634
Come out, it's hot

724
00:38:26,137 --> 00:38:28,306
[cell phone ringing sound]

725
00:38:30,266 --> 00:38:32,310
- [Pang! phut! - Laundry] - Dad, call me.

726
00:38:45,323 --> 00:38:46,282
uh

727
00:38:46,365 --> 00:38:49,118
Oppa, oppa, can you see me now?

728
00:38:49,952 --> 00:38:50,995
Oh, I'm good

729
00:38:52,204 --> 00:38:53,497
Where should I see it?

730
00:38:53,581 --> 00:38:54,707
See you at my house

731
00:38:54,790 --> 00:38:57,209
- [Nervous music] - Oh, no, no, I'm going out.

732
00:38:57,293 --> 00:38:59,045
