My dad has urgent business, so let’s go to his house for a while.

739
00:39:31,535 --> 00:39:32,536
[Soyoung] Ah, why!

740
00:39:32,620 --> 00:39:35,456
[Seungmin] Oh, just this one time. It’s not a joke. Just this one time.

741
00:39:35,539 --> 00:39:36,665
Just once, just once

742
00:39:38,334 --> 00:39:39,335
