744
00:39:51,097 --> 00:39:52,807
Wouldn’t it be a bit too much starting in broad daylight?

745
00:39:52,890 --> 00:39:55,017
Your mother-in-law only looks after the kids during the day.

746
00:39:56,519 --> 00:39:57,812
Why are you so pretty today?

747
