753
00:40:11,450 --> 00:40:13,119
- What is it, your mother-in-law? - [Bangtang - Moon]

754
00:40:14,995 --> 00:40:16,622
No, I suddenly had something urgent come up.

755
00:40:16,705 --> 00:40:18,249
