I should say, ‘Thank you for taking care of me, uncle.’

759
00:40:23,337 --> 00:40:24,880
thank you for your care

760
00:40:24,964 --> 00:40:26,757
Uh, stay there in a bit and your dad will come pick you up.

761
00:40:26,841 --> 00:40:27,883
uh, thank you

