Hey, hey, hey, hey, hey, hey!

763
00:40:31,137 --> 00:40:32,471
Can't you see what I'm wearing right now?

764
00:40:33,055 --> 00:40:35,474
hey! I also left my baby with my mother-in-law, Mr.

765
00:40:35,558 --> 00:40:37,560
How is your mother-in-law? I love you, Wondae-ya

766
00:40:37,643 --> 00:40:39,019
Take me to the academy by 5 o'clock

767
00:40:39,103 --> 00:40:41,313
I love you my wife!

768
00:40:41,897 --> 00:40:44,525
what? 10 minutes? Isn't the car blocked?

769
00:40:46,068 --> 00:40:47,445
Oh, wow, thank goodness.

770
00:40:49,405 --> 00:40:51,782
Oh, should we drink wine today? In a mood?

771
00:40:52,575 --> 00:40:54,827
Uh, ah, drinking beer only fills my stomach.

772
00:40:54,910 --> 00:40:57,788
Do you want to go to the bathroom often and bring something back?

773
00:40:57,872 --> 00:40:59,498
Uh, I'll send you the address.

774
00:40:59,582 --> 00:41:01,625
Uh, uh, uh yes, yes, yes

