00:54:49,077 --> 00:54:51,121
[Urgent music]

1028
00:54:51,955 --> 00:54:53,707
[cell phone vibrates]

1029
00:54:55,709 --> 00:54:57,085
Oh, why aren't you answering the phone?

1030
00:54:59,963 --> 00:55:02,173
Me, So, Soyoung!

1031
00:55:02,257 --> 00:55:03,508
[Jiwoo’s husband] Seungho, it’s been a while.

1032
00:55:03,591 --> 00:55:04,551
[Seungho] Yes, hello

1033
00:55:04,634 --> 00:55:06,052
- [Jiwoo’s husband] How are you? - [Seungho] Ah, yes

1034
00:55:06,136 --> 00:55:08,221
Soyoung, where are you going?

1035
00:55:08,304 --> 00:55:10,849
Of course I'll go home. What kind of amusement park would I go to?

1036
00:55:10,932 --> 00:55:13,601
Ah, uh, my uncle... do you want me to buy you some ice cream, ice cream?

1037
00:55:13,685 --> 00:55:14,978
No, I'm going to lose weight

1038
00:55:18,314 --> 00:55:19,983
Hey, why are you losing weight so I’ll buy you ice cream?

1039
00:55:20,066 --> 00:55:20,942
You like ice cream.

1040
00:55:21,026 --> 00:55:22,902
[Soyoung] My uncle keeps saying that, so I gain more weight.

1041
00:55:22,986 --> 00:55:23,987
I'm going to lose weight

1042
00:55:24,070 --> 00:55:25,488
- Ah, come here, ugh - [Soyoung] Ah, what is it?

1043
00:55:25,572 --> 00:55:28,033
[Seungho] Teacher, please teach our Soyoung some self-defense skills.

1044
00:55:28,116 --> 00:55:29,534
The world is so ugly these days

1045
00:55:29,617 --> 00:55:31,286
Our Soyoung is also capable of self-defense on her own...

1046
00:55:31,369 --> 00:55:32,370
- [Crumple] - Ah, ah, ah!

1047
00:55:32,454 --> 00:55:34,122
- I have a blue belt in Taekwondo? - Oh, okay, okay.

1048
00:55:34,205 --> 00:55:35,832
Do you think your uncle should learn self-defense?

1049
00:55:35,915 --> 00:55:37,751
[Seungho] It hurts, it hurts, it hurts! Ah, ugh

1050
00:55:38,418 --> 00:55:39,669
- Ugh, huh? - Yes.

1051
00:55:39,753 --> 00:55:41,296
Seungho needs to learn self-defense.

1052
00:55:41,379 --> 00:55:43,214
- No, Soyoung is going up now... - Come to the gym starting tomorrow.

1053
00:55:43,298 --> 00:55:45,383
- [Seungho] Ah, arm, arm, arm - Gyu that will come out, Gyu that won't come out?

1054
00:55:45,467 --> 00:55:46,468
[Seungmin] Is it difficult?

1055
00:55:48,595 --> 00:55:49,804
[Bona] I haven’t tried it before

1056
00:55:53,058 --> 00:55:54,726
[Beep beep - door lock button sound]

1057
00:55:54,809 --> 00:55:55,894
[Tirik - Door Lock]

1058
00:55:56,853 --> 00:55:57,854
[Tak-Moon]

1059
00:55:59,814 --> 00:56:01,066
hello

1060
00:56:02,692 --> 00:56:04,069
who is this?

1061
00:56:04,152 --> 00:56:06,154
[humorous music]

1062
00:56:06,780 --> 00:56:07,655
You're Aunt Bona, right?

1063
00:56:09,407 --> 00:56:10,575
I'm Soyoung

1064
00:56:12,994 --> 00:56:14,079
Is Seungmin Choi there?

1065
00:56:15,246 --> 00:56:17,123
uh? Oh, I went to the bathroom.

1066
00:56:18,583 --> 00:56:20,585
[TV sound plays]

1067
00:56:21,544 --> 00:56:22,879
- [Click - Moon] - [Seungmin's refreshing breath]

1068
00:56:22,962 --> 00:56:23,963
[Bona] Uh...

1069
00:56:25,924 --> 00:56:26,966
- what? - [Seungmin] What?

1070
00:56:29,803 --> 00:56:30,804
[Intense sound effect]

1071
00:56:36,267 --> 00:56:37,268
What are you staring at?

1072
00:56:37,769 --> 00:56:38,978
You don’t even say hello to your younger brother?

1073
00:56:39,771 --> 00:56:41,231
I told you I was here

1074
00:56:41,314 --> 00:56:42,607
[Clearly] Oppa

1075
00:56:42,690 --> 00:56:43,900
[Whistle sound effect]

1076
00:56:44,567 --> 00:56:45,568
[Bona] Oppa?

1077
00:56:48,321 --> 00:56:49,656
uh? uh

1078
00:56:50,532 --> 00:56:51,533
[Bona] Uh...

1079
00:56:53,785 --> 00:56:55,370
- how have you been doing? - huh

1080
00:56:57,205 --> 00:56:58,998
The house has changed a lot

1081
00:56:59,999 --> 00:57:02,127
It’s so different from the last time you came, isn’t it?

1082
00:57:02,961 --> 00:57:04,838
[Ding Dong - Doorbell]

1083
00:57:04,921 --> 00:57:07,090
- [Soyoung] Who is here? - Sushi is here!

1084
00:57:07,173 --> 00:57:08,341
Um, can you get me some sushi?

1085
00:57:08,967 --> 00:57:09,843
[Small] I'm sorry

1086
00:57:17,517 --> 00:57:18,852
[Click click - door]

1087
00:57:19,811 --> 00:57:20,937
- [Tirik - Door Lock] - Soyoungah

1088
00:57:21,855 --> 00:57:23,064
You were supposed to stay at mom's house today.

1089
00:57:23,148 --> 00:57:25,191
[Soyoung] I was angry, but now I’m relieved

1090
00:57:26,276 --> 00:57:28,194
- If you don’t like it, I’ll go. - No.

1091
00:57:28,278 --> 00:57:29,487
I'm sorry dad, my daughter

1092
00:57:30,280 --> 00:57:33,032
I hid my daughter’s existence just to try dating.

1093
00:57:33,992 --> 00:57:34,826
Like a fool

1094
00:57:35,827 --> 00:57:36,870
That's it for me, I'm done

1095
00:57:36,953 --> 00:57:38,121
- I'm going to confess everything today - No.

1096
00:57:38,913 --> 00:57:40,498
I've been reading about trauma

1097
00:57:40,582 --> 00:57:43,209
If I tell you the truth, there are three scenarios:

1098
00:57:43,293 --> 00:57:44,294
I thought about it all

1099
00:57:45,462 --> 00:57:46,337
uh?

1100
00:57:46,421 --> 00:57:48,423
[Interesting music]

1101
00:57:49,757 --> 00:57:51,384
Bona, this is my daughter.

1102
00:57:52,218 --> 00:57:53,094
You're kidding, right?

1103
00:57:54,971 --> 00:57:55,930
It's true

1104
00:57:58,057 --> 00:58:00,101
What a crazy bastard, Mr. Lee.

1105
00:58:05,982 --> 00:58:07,317
Bona, this is my daughter.

1106
00:58:07,984 --> 00:58:08,860
You're kidding, right?

1107
00:58:08,943 --> 00:58:10,069
- It's true - Merong

1108
00:58:12,113 --> 00:58:14,282
ah! eww!

1109
00:58:15,074 --> 00:58:17,160
iced coffee! Ah, snow!

1110
00:58:17,243 --> 00:58:18,995
Ouch! ah!

1111
00:58:26,085 --> 00:58:27,045
[Crying] She’s my daughter.

1112
00:58:27,128 --> 00:58:28,129
You're kidding, right?

1113
00:58:28,713 --> 00:58:30,340
I'm really, really, really sorry.

1114
00:58:30,423 --> 00:58:31,549
melong, melong

1115
00:58:31,633 --> 00:58:33,218
What the ♪

1116
00:58:37,138 --> 00:58:40,016
Me, me, me, me long, me long

1117
00:58:43,603 --> 00:58:46,689
[Bona] Oh my God!

1118
00:58:46,773 --> 00:58:48,525
- [Slowing down sound effect] - No!

1119
00:58:48,608 --> 00:58:52,070
See you!

1120
00:58:54,906 --> 00:58:56,616
If you like that lady, listen to me.

1121
00:58:58,117 --> 00:59:01,037
Breakups are painful, so I don’t want my dad to be hurt.

1122
00:59:01,704 --> 00:59:03,164
What are you planning to do next?

1123
00:59:03,248 --> 00:59:05,291
From now on, there will be no dad

1124
00:59:05,375 --> 00:59:06,793
As if there is no Santa Claus

1125
00:59:06,876 --> 00:59:09,295
- There is Santa - I know everything, there is no Santa.

1126
00:59:11,756 --> 00:59:14,634
[Soyoung] My dad is a total playboy.

1127
00:59:14,717 --> 00:59:16,094
I had babies here and there.

1128
00:59:17,136 --> 00:59:18,846
- About nine to ten people? - [Humorous music]

1129
00:59:19,681 --> 00:59:21,349
- Right, brother? - nine people

1130
00:59:22,308 --> 00:59:24,644
[Soyoung] I am the youngest and my brother is the eldest.

1131
00:59:24,727 --> 00:59:26,271
All mothers are different

1132
00:59:27,272 --> 00:59:29,941
Then at what age did you give birth?

1133
00:59:30,024 --> 00:59:32,652
I don't know, curly old man.

1134
00:59:33,319 --> 00:59:35,363
- He was around 7, 80. - 7, 8...

1135
00:59:35,446 --> 00:59:36,364
[Soyoung sniffles]

1136
00:59:36,447 --> 00:59:40,368
After giving birth, he left.

1137
00:59:41,119 --> 00:59:43,621
Poor mom lives alone.

1138
00:59:43,705 --> 00:59:47,333
I'm pregnant and feeling uncomfortable.

1139
00:59:47,417 --> 00:59:48,751
Is this your father's child?

1140
00:59:48,835 --> 00:59:51,588
No, it's someone else's kid.

1141
00:59:51,671 --> 00:59:54,215
My dad is in a nursing home now.

1142
00:59:54,299 --> 00:59:57,218
They say he's dating another grandmother there too.

1143
00:59:57,302 --> 00:59:59,846
Don't talk about my dad like that

1144
00:59:59,929 --> 01:00:02,473
So where are you going to sleep today?

1145
01:00:02,557 --> 01:00:04,434
Here, what about the lady?

1146
01:00:05,351 --> 01:00:06,811
Ugh, I forgot to tell you.

1147
01:00:08,313 --> 01:00:09,647
I need to rest for a few days because my mom is sick.

1148
01:00:09,731 --> 01:00:12,358
I'm alone and I'm begging you to do me a favor...

1149
01:00:12,442 --> 01:00:14,068
[Soyoung sobs]

1150
01:00:14,152 --> 01:00:15,403
[Soyoung/crying] My mom

1151
01:00:16,321 --> 01:00:18,489
Poor, you're not feeling well.

1152
01:00:21,409 --> 01:00:23,119
- Wait a minute - [Seungmin] Oh

1153
01:00:26,080 --> 01:00:27,081
[Soyoung/Small] It’s because of the wasabi

1154
01:00:27,165 --> 01:00:29,042
Did you eat wasabi? quickly, quickly, quickly

1155
01:00:34,964 --> 01:00:36,049
Oh, I don't understand.

1156
01:00:36,841 --> 01:00:39,510
Ah, my nine-year-old brother suddenly appears.

1157
01:00:41,137 --> 01:00:42,055
[Seungmin] I’m sorry

1158
01:00:42,847 --> 01:00:44,891
The fact that my father was a libertine is nothing to brag about.

1159
01:00:45,933 --> 01:00:48,728
The age difference is so big that we hardly ever see each other.

1160
01:00:48,811 --> 01:00:50,772
Oh, their mom made a mess of it and it ended up like this.

1161
01:00:50,855 --> 01:00:52,231
[Continued drumming]

1162
01:00:52,315 --> 01:00:53,316
[Bona] Ah...

1163
01:00:56,611 --> 01:00:58,237
You know the book I gave you last time, ‘No Kids’?

1164
01:00:59,155 --> 01:01:00,198
I read it all

1165
01:01:01,449 --> 01:01:02,492
How was it?

1166
01:01:06,037 --> 01:01:07,163
It's hard for the kids

1167
01:01:08,247 --> 01:01:11,542
It's noisy, hectic, and there's a lot to take care of.

1168
01:01:11,626 --> 01:01:13,336
Still, just in case...

1169
01:01:14,837 --> 01:01:16,464
It could get better, right?

1170
01:01:16,547 --> 01:01:17,799
People change, right?

1171
01:01:18,424 --> 01:01:20,885
I don’t think I’ll change, because I don’t like it.

1172
01:01:20,968 --> 01:01:21,844
Isn't it?

1173
01:01:26,349 --> 01:01:28,434
You said you were jealous of me realizing my dream, right?

1174
01:01:28,518 --> 01:01:30,019
Yeah, cool

1175
01:01:30,770 --> 01:01:32,897
There were a lot of things I had to give up because of that dream.

1176
01:01:33,564 --> 01:01:35,316
Marriage and raising children are one of them.

1177
01:01:35,400 --> 01:01:37,610
But I like my life now

1178
01:01:37,694 --> 01:01:39,445
I want to live like that?

1179
01:01:40,279 --> 01:01:41,280
Good

1180
01:01:42,323 --> 01:01:45,076
[Bona] Someday, when I'm older, 30 years later

1181
01:01:45,159 --> 01:01:48,746
I don't care if people tell me I've wasted my life

1182
01:01:48,830 --> 01:01:50,289
Ha, I lived in vain.

1183
01:01:50,373 --> 01:01:52,291
If you grow old without children, your life will be wasted.

1184
01:01:52,375 --> 01:01:53,918
There are people who think

1185
01:01:54,001 --> 01:01:56,713
It's my freedom to choose whether to have a child or not.

1186
01:01:56,796 --> 01:01:58,256
It's not a defect?

1187
01:01:58,339 --> 01:02:00,883
[Doo-doo-dong bang-drum]

1188
01:02:02,343 --> 01:02:03,803
Are you going to buy it or not?

1189
01:02:03,886 --> 01:02:05,096
You're not going to buy it?

1190
01:02:05,179 --> 01:02:07,306
Hey, go, go, go, go

1191
01:02:07,390 --> 01:02:09,225
[Seungho] Oh, just come next time, come next time

1192
01:02:09,308 --> 01:02:12,019
And the kids hate me anyway

1193
01:02:12,937 --> 01:02:13,980
no way

1194
01:02:15,148 --> 01:02:17,316
Our feelings are the same

1195
01:02:17,400 --> 01:02:18,985
No, some bastards...

1196
01:02:19,068 --> 01:02:21,070
No, uh, what kind of kids do that?

1197
01:02:21,154 --> 01:02:23,573
Just kids, everything.

1198
01:02:23,656 --> 01:02:24,866
- Everything? - [Interesting Music]

1199
01:02:24,949 --> 01:02:26,492
[noisy]

1200
01:02:30,079 --> 01:02:31,080
What are you doing playing?

1201
01:02:32,457 --> 01:02:33,791
hi

1202
01:02:34,333 --> 01:02:36,878
Ugh, I hate it!

1203
01:02:37,587 --> 01:02:39,213
Look, let's go

1204
01:02:39,297 --> 01:02:41,007
Oh, come on, let's do it one more time.

1205
01:02:41,591 --> 01:02:42,633
This doesn't make sense

1206
01:02:43,301 --> 01:02:44,427
How's the baby over there?

1207
01:02:47,096 --> 01:02:48,139
Baby, you're pretty

1208
01:02:48,222 --> 01:02:49,390
[Ugh]

1209
01:02:51,184 --> 01:02:53,060
Did you see it? I said I couldn't do it.

1210
01:02:53,978 --> 01:02:55,188
Wow, how can this happen?

1211
01:02:55,772 --> 01:02:58,149
Uh, don't cry, right, right

1212
01:02:58,232 --> 01:02:59,317
[Laughs] Right, right.

1213
01:03:00,318 --> 01:03:01,319
hi

1214
01:03:01,402 --> 01:03:02,820
[Ugh]

1215
01:03:06,073 --> 01:03:08,242
♪ She's so stupid ♪

1216
01:03:08,326 --> 01:03:10,787
♪ Oh, she's so ugly ♪

1217
01:03:10,870 --> 01:03:15,124
♪ She's skinny and even farts loudly ♪

1218
01:03:18,920 --> 01:03:19,837
What do you think, brother?

1219
01:03:19,921 --> 01:03:22,548
I think the lyrics are too inappropriate to sing at an arts festival.

1220
01:03:23,382 --> 01:03:24,383
What about Aunt Bona?

1221
01:03:25,676 --> 01:03:26,594
auntie?

1222
01:03:27,887 --> 01:03:28,721
Then what do you say?

1223
01:03:29,680 --> 01:03:31,057
I should call you sister

1224
01:03:31,140 --> 01:03:32,642
Oh, sure, sister.

1225
01:03:33,392 --> 01:03:34,811
Then sister, this time

1226
01:03:34,894 --> 01:03:38,481
Would you like to listen to the song ‘I Really, Really Hate You’?

1227
01:03:38,564 --> 01:03:39,565
[Jiying - Guitar]

1228
01:03:39,649 --> 01:03:41,651
[Quiet music - headphones]

1229
01:03:50,993 --> 01:03:51,994
[Soyoung’s sigh]

1230
01:03:54,497 --> 01:03:55,998
Why are you so quiet, are you angry?

1231
01:03:56,999 --> 01:03:59,252
[Soyoung] No, it’s because I miss you

1232
01:04:00,628 --> 01:04:01,671
miss? what?

1233
01:04:01,754 --> 01:04:03,297
In the past

1234
01:04:04,048 --> 01:04:07,635
When mom, dad, and I lived together

1235
01:04:08,719 --> 01:04:10,263
I didn't even have a younger brother at that time.

1236
01:04:10,972 --> 01:04:12,348
Dad doesn't have a girlfriend.

1237
01:04:13,391 --> 01:04:14,684
It was really good

1238
01:04:15,768 --> 01:04:17,854
But having a younger sibling is a wonderful thing.

1239
01:04:18,479 --> 01:04:19,814
Don't say that strange thing

1240
01:04:22,108 --> 01:04:23,776
That's what life is like, whatever.

1241
01:04:24,527 --> 01:04:25,528
We're all here

1242
01:04:26,445 --> 01:04:28,281
Uncle Seungho will come pick you up later.

1243
01:04:28,364 --> 01:04:30,366
Dad has to go on a business trip to the countryside.

1244
01:04:30,449 --> 01:04:31,993
- Let's go. - What are we going with?

1245
01:04:32,618 --> 01:04:33,786
Dad just go

1246
01:04:34,745 --> 01:04:36,664
Why are you embarrassed to go together?

1247
01:04:36,747 --> 01:04:39,333
Of course not, don't look at me like that

1248
01:04:40,042 --> 01:04:41,460
I'm all grown up now

1249
01:04:42,920 --> 01:04:44,797
Ha, that's life, well

1250
01:04:45,339 --> 01:04:46,382
I'll go

1251
01:04:48,634 --> 01:04:49,635
[Seungmin] Soyoungah

1252
01:04:50,261 --> 01:04:51,178
[Tap - car door]

1253
01:04:51,262 --> 01:04:53,598
[Employee] Okay, just use the keyboard for a moment.

1254
01:04:54,348 --> 01:04:55,433
[cell phone ringing sound]

1255
01:04:55,516 --> 01:04:56,434
[Seungmin] Please do that.

1256
01:04:56,517 --> 01:04:57,351
- Just a moment - [Employee] Yes.

1257
01:04:58,311 --> 01:04:59,312
Uh, why?

1258
01:04:59,395 --> 01:05:00,438
[Seungho] Hyung, I got into an accident.

1259
01:05:00,521 --> 01:05:02,273
what? Are you hurt?

1260
01:05:02,356 --> 01:05:04,233
No, I wasn't hurt.

1261
01:05:04,317 --> 01:05:07,111
Ah, I'm not in a situation where Soyoung is going to pick me up right now, uh.

1262
01:05:07,194 --> 01:05:08,154
Oh, I can't do that.

1263
01:05:08,237 --> 01:05:09,530
I came to Incheon to get a keyboard right now.

1264
01:05:09,614 --> 01:05:10,656
[Interesting music]

1265
01:05:10,740 --> 01:05:12,283
Oh, okay, just hang up for now.

1266
01:05:12,992 --> 01:05:14,035
Uh, hang up, hang up

1267
01:05:15,870 --> 01:05:17,204
- Wait a minute. - Oh, yeah.

1268
01:05:18,122 --> 01:05:19,832
Did you lock the door? Seungmin goes up again

1269
01:05:20,833 --> 01:05:22,585
I also put my phone on airplane mode.

1270
01:05:23,127 --> 01:05:25,254
- [Atmospheric music] - That plane

1271
01:05:25,338 --> 01:05:26,464
Where are you going?

1272
01:05:26,547 --> 01:05:27,590
That plane?

1273
01:05:30,426 --> 01:05:31,677
I'm not coming back from Hong Kong

1274
01:05:33,471 --> 01:05:35,306
Ah, I think this guy doesn't accept it on purpose.

1275
01:05:35,389 --> 01:05:37,350
[Interesting music]

1276
01:05:37,433 --> 01:05:39,727
- [Atmospheric music] - [Mobile phone vibrating sound]

1277
01:05:39,810 --> 01:05:40,895
[Jiwoo’s husband] Take it.

1278
01:05:41,687 --> 01:05:43,022
[Jiwoo] Ah, that’s enough

1279
01:05:43,105 --> 01:05:45,608
Are these people opting out as a group or what?

